data.description: Built in 2020, End Corner property with beautiful upgrades including ceramic tile flooring and white plantation shutters throughout the home. The Kitchen offers; Samsung stainless steel appliances, granite counters, breakfast bar, ceramic tile flooring and an eat in kitchen. The open concept design of the main floor flows seamlessly into the dining room and living area.  Just outside is a great shady retreat with a paver patio lounging area to enjoy. Upstairs features 3 generous bedrooms with separate laundry room outfitted with a Samsung washer and dryer set. The sprawling primary bedroom is a suite made for a king or queen! His & Her walk in closets, separate vanities with granite countertops and an immense walk in shower, separate toilet room and linen closet. Secondary bedrooms are oversized and offer walk in closets and share a Jack-n-Jill bathroom with separate granite counter topped vanity from toilet and shower room. Great community with pool, park and dog park.
